For the norm, the associated norm on $E \otimes_F D$ would be $N_E(x) = q_E(x)$ for $x \neq 0$. This is multiplicative: $N_E(xy) = q_E(xy) = q_E(x)q_E(y) = N_E(x)N_E(y)$.

